data.description: Elegance at its finest! 2800 sqft feet all on one level.  This meticulously maintained 5 bedroom, study and 4 bath home is wonderfully located in the prominent Rio de Bella Addition within the Westmoore school district and boasts nearly an acre lot with a brand new 30x30 insulated shop with full electric including a 220 outlet. Split floor leads into a large bonus room that can be 5th bedroom/Mother-in-law suite. Open floor plan, gas fireplace with beautiful mantle, wood-look tile, walk-in pantry, double oven with gas range, farmhouse sink located on a large island. Newer carpet in all bedrooms.  Large Laundry room with extra storage.  Grand Master Suite includes his and her sinks, soaking tub and walk in shower. Extra large closet with third row shelving. Oversized 3 car garage with extra storage. Expansive covered patio area with extended pergola.  Great neighborhood. Neighborhood pond is across the street from the house. Refrigerators and zero turn mower can stay with acceptable offer. Price based on a 2023 Appraisal.
